<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 03:12:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国经济将为世界复苏提供强劲动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economy-will-provide-strong-driving-force-world-recovery-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国最高立法委员赵乐际周四表示，中国经济将为世界复苏提供强大动力，并承诺中国开放的大门只会越开越大。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economy-will-provide-strong-driving-force-world-recovery-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾认为无论谁赢得选举，美国的支持都不会改变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-sees-us-support-unchanged-no-matter-who-wins-election-2024-03-28/</link><description>台湾外交部周四表示，相信无论谁赢得总统选举，美国的支持都将保持不变，但随着竞选活动的升温，台湾将继续警惕台湾与中国问题被“操纵”的情况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:45:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-sees-us-support-unchanged-no-matter-who-wins-election-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>日元受到干预观察；亚洲股市低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-28/</link><description>日元周四跌至近几十年来的最低水平，尽管日本当局的干预威胁让投资者对将日元推至新低持谨慎态度，而亚洲股市在美国关键通胀数据公布之前下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国设定的人民币汇率远强于市场预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-sets-yuan-much-stronger-fixing-than-markets-expected-2024-03-28/</link><description>随着当局加大力度防止人民币大幅贬值，中国央行将人民币汇率设定为近五个月来的最大差距。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-sets-yuan-much-stronger-fixing-than-markets-expected-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望荷兰确保光刻机贸易“正常”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hopes-netherlands-will-ensure-normal-lithography-machine-trade-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国商务部部长王文涛表示，中方希望荷兰支持企业履行合同义务，确保光刻机贸易“正常”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:50:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hopes-netherlands-will-ensure-normal-lithography-machine-trade-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>小米在中国汽车的艰难时期进军电动汽车领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-set-plunge-into-evs-tricky-time-china-autos-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国小米将于周四推出备受期待的电动汽车（EV），届时将公布定价并开始接受订单，这标志着这家电子公司进军汽车领域。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 23:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-set-plunge-into-evs-tricky-time-china-autos-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日元大坝已决口，但并未决堤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-27/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 21:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国新制裁针对朝鲜军事财政</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-north-korea-sanctions-target-individuals-russia-china-uae-based-firms-2024-03-27/</link><description>美国周三宣布对位于俄罗斯、中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国的六名个人和两个实体实施制裁，指责他们向朝鲜的武器计划提供资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-north-korea-sanctions-target-individuals-russia-china-uae-based-firms-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯公司开始在前 Stellantis 工厂生产雪铁龙</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russian-company-starts-citroen-production-former-stellantis-factory-2024-03-27/</link><description>俄罗斯汽车技术公司周三表示，已开始在莫斯科南部的一家工厂批量组装雪铁龙 C5 Aircross 车型，该工厂原属于 Stellantis 公司，这些汽车将于 5 月起在经销商处销售。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russian-company-starts-citroen-production-former-stellantis-factory-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促盟国禁止公司为中国提供关键芯片制造工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-is-urging-allies-bar-firms-servicing-key-chipmaking-tools-china-2024-03-27/</link><description>美国商务部官员周三表示，美国正在要求盟国阻止国内公司为中国客户提供某些芯片制造工具，同时加大力度限制中国的芯片制造能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-is-urging-allies-bar-firms-servicing-key-chipmaking-tools-china-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰首相在北京向中国习近平提出网络间谍问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/beijing-dutch-pm-raises-cyberespionage-with-chinas-xi-2024-03-27/</link><description>荷兰首相马克·吕特表示，他在周三与国家主席习近平的会谈中讨论了荷兰归咎于中国政府的网络间谍事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/beijing-dutch-pm-raises-cyberespionage-with-chinas-xi-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：第一量子高管与中国官员讨论投资和有争议的铜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/first-quantum-execs-discuss-investment-disputed-copper-with-chinese-officials-2024-03-27/</link><description>三名知情人士称，加拿大矿业公司第一量子矿业公司的高管上周会见了中国政府官员，讨论了涉及最大投资者江西铜业的融资和业务选择。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/first-quantum-execs-discuss-investment-disputed-copper-with-chinese-officials-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>智利矿业部长敦促SQM和天齐解决争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chiles-mining-minister-urges-sqm-tianqi-resolve-spat-2024-03-27/</link><description>智利矿业部长周三敦促智利矿商SQM和该公司大股东中国天齐锂业解决持续的争端，但没有介入他们的私人问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chiles-mining-minister-urges-sqm-tianqi-resolve-spat-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>驻菲律宾外国记者谴责中国涉嫌操纵视频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-correspondents-philippines-condemn-china-over-claims-video-manipulation-2024-03-27/</link><description>驻马尼拉的外国记者周三驳斥了中国的说法，即菲律宾让记者篡改在南海补给任务期间拍摄的视频，使其看起来像“受害者”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-correspondents-philippines-condemn-china-over-claims-video-manipulation-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪的目标是年销量增长 20% - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicle-maker-byd-targets-20-jump-annual-sales-2024-03-27/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪制定了 2024 年销量目标 360 万辆，较去年破纪录的销量增长 20%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicle-maker-byd-targets-20-jump-annual-sales-2024-03-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>